<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="astonish-vt">astonish <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'stɒnɪʃ/    美 /ə'stɑːnɪʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使大为惊讶；使惊骇：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What he said at the meeting astonished everybody present.
他在会上所说的话令在场的所有人感到吃惊。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>astonishing /ə'stɑːnɪʃɪŋ/ adj <br />
astonishment /ə'stɑːnɪʃmənt/ n [U]   </p></div>